title: Tiamo's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Middle Eastern, Greek, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Veg-friendly cafe offering a wide range of vegetarian and vegan choices. The tapas menu includes smoked aubergine dip, large olives, hummus, salad, garlic pita bread, falafel, soup, stuffed grape leaves; there are also sandwichesbas well as hot daily specials such as vegetable lasagne; also pastries, tea and coffee. The interior is cozy with wood panels.
